                        "text": "claw +24 (<a aonid=\"170\" game-obj=\"Traits\"><u>agile</u></a>, <a aonid=\"192\" game-obj=\"Traits\"><u>reach 10 feet</u></a>), <b>Damage</b> 2d10+13 slashing plus drain life",
